{"tid":900024,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲仲未搞掂呢個病","createTime":"2018-11-13T02:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T11:11:15.000Z","uid":161343,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"45d60422c96408fc6040813c7b946dbd83bae204","tid":900024,"uid":161343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:07:45.000Z","msg":"當看差唔多14歲果陣 <br />\n醫生證實我有牛皮癬(銀屑病)<br />\n患者頭皮 指甲 手踭 耳背都會受影響<br />\n但我已經算好彩 淨係頭皮同指甲<br />\n細細個就話免疫能力差d先有呢d病<br />\n點知都成20歲仲未好返<br />\n我一直都有睇醫生 試過有一排d頭皮好左好多<br />\n點知過一排個病又會岀返黎<br />\n其實我覺得佢真係好影響我生活<br />\n青少年最注重外表 每次剪頭髮都好唔情願<br />\n因為我頭皮會紅色而且仲有好似魚鱗既頭皮不停甩落黎 我知好核突 但係你估我想架咩<br />\n我最嚴重係個頭後面 所以同人傾計或者有人行過<br />\n我下意識會正面對住佢 驚佢睇到 真係好影響身心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7258bbf5aa2c7d904a0e1f66441298db0844fb2e","tid":900024,"uid":161343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:08:23.000Z","msg":"好想醫好呢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6535282ac404662cd01283513cebace3631c40e4","tid":900024,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"劍客西門吹雪"},{"pid":"5dcaad66cede2ddb2b51b5190f46eacb5c0efb26","tid":900024,"uid":161343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:12:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人有親戚或朋友有呢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但願世界上再無呢個病"},{"pid":"90a0c9cc3dcd61988e333d7f9a2a33637efb6165","tid":900024,"uid":161343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:14:16.000Z","msg":"轉季乾燥或壓力情緒都會令病情嚴重<br />\n但係有呢個病點會無壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef659960a0bec6ef67bbd928376c55ed2713e05","tid":900024,"uid":70634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:49:44.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n由小四都依家23歲 情況都係時好時壞"},{"pid":"156b2aa0ca6f3922c510d72867df2e